{"id":547077,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abbas_Kiarostami","text":"Abbas Kiarostami (; 22 June 1940 \u2013 4 July 2016) was an Iranian movie director, screenwriter, photographer and movie producer.\nHe was known for making documentaries or short movies. His best known works are the \"Koker trilogy\" (1987\u201394), \"Close-Up\" (1990), \"Taste of Cherry\" (1997) and \"The Wind Will Carry Us\" (1999). In his later works, \"Certified Copy\" (2010) and \"Like Someone in Love\".\nKiarostami died at a Paris hospital on 4 July 2016 from gastrointestinal cancer, aged 76.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Iran","surface_form":"Iran","offset":55},{"uri":"Movie_director","surface_form":"movie director","offset":63},{"uri":"Screenwriter","surface_form":"screenwriter","offset":79},{"uri":"Photographer","surface_form":"photographer","offset":93},{"uri":"Movie_producer","surface_form":"movie producer","offset":110},{"uri":"Documentaries","surface_form":"documentaries","offset":150},{"uri":"Short_movie","surface_form":"short movie","offset":167},{"uri":"Koker_trilogy","surface_form":"Koker trilogy","offset":211},{"uri":"Close-Up_(1990_movie)","surface_form":"Close-Up","offset":238},{"uri":"Taste_of_Cherry","surface_form":"Taste of Cherry","offset":257},{"uri":"The_Wind_Will_Carry_Us","surface_form":"The Wind Will Carry Us","offset":286},{"uri":"Certified_Copy_(movie)","surface_form":"Certified Copy","offset":339},{"uri":"Like_Someone_in_Love_(movie)","surface_form":"Like Someone in Love","offset":367},{"uri":"Paris","surface_form":"Paris","offset":411},{"uri":"Gastrointestinal_cancer","surface_form":"gastrointestinal cancer","offset":446}]}